<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Warp – Autonomous Customer Support Agent</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Autonomous customer support operations agent. Triage tickets, route intelligently, draft replies, and keep support operations disciplined across 8+ helpdesk platforms.">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', sans-serif;
            background: #05070d;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Background effects */
        .bg-layer {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: -10;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15), transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08), transparent 40%),
                        linear-gradient(180deg, #05070d 0%, #071018 45%, #030507 100%);
        }

        .grid-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: -9;
            opacity: 0.08;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
                            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 56px 56px;
        }

        .glow-top {
            position: fixed;
            left: 50%;
            top: 4rem;
            height: 420px;
            width: 720px;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border-radius: 100%;
            background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.06);
            filter: blur(80px);
            z-index: -8;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            background: rgba(5, 7, 13, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .header-container {
            max-width: 80rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            height: 4rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 2.25rem;
            height: 2.25rem;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
            background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #a5f3fc;
            box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .cta-button {
            border-radius: 9999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
            background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
            padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #a5f3fc;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.12);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.16);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            max-width: 80rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 4rem);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: #a5f3fc;
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 0.5rem;
            height: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            background: #6ee7b7;
            box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.8);
        }

        h1 {
            max-width: 65rem;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #a5f3fc, #5eead4, #fde68a);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-description {
            max-width: 48rem;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            background: #a5f3fc;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f172a;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 42px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.24);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #67e8f9;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        }

        .proof-points {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .proof-point {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .checkmark {
            color: #6ee7b7;
        }

        /* Terminal Section */
        .terminal {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 80rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
            padding: 0.75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .terminal-inner {
            border-radius: 1.4rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            background: #070b12;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .terminal-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .terminal-title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .live-badge {
            border-radius: 9999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.2);
            background: rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.1);
            padding: 0.25rem 0.625rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #6ee7b7;
        }

        .command-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        }

        .command-card {
            border-radius: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .command {
            color: #a5f3fc;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        .command-output {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        /* Section styles */
        .section {
            max-width: 80rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: #fde68a;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.75rem);
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: white;
            max-width: 48rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Grid layouts */
        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        }

        .grid-3 {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        }

        .grid-4 {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        }

        /* Card styles */
        .card {
            border-radius: 1.6rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.25);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 2.75rem;
            height: 2.75rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
            background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #a5f3fc;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .card-body {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        /* Integration badges */
        .integrations {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .integration-badge {
            border-radius: 9999px;
            background: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.1);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 80rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #06b6d4;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #67e8f9;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            .hero-description {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .button-group {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .proof-points {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.75rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-layer"></div>
    <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
    <div class="glow-top"></div>

    <header>
        <div class="header-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">W</div>
                <div class="logo-text">Warp</div>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/ruimachado-orbit/warp" class="cta-button">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="badge">
            <span class="status-dot"></span>
            Support Operations Online
        </div>

        <h1>
            Autonomous support ops. <span class="gradient-text">Zero manual triage.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-description">
            Warp is an AI-powered customer support operations agent. It watches tickets across 8+ helpdesk platforms, classifies by category/severity/sentiment, routes intelligently, drafts replies, and keeps your support machine disciplined.
        </p>

        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="#capabilities" class="btn-primary">
                Explore capabilities →
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/ruimachado-orbit/warp" class="btn-secondary">
                See on GitHub
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="proof-points">
            <div class="proof-point">
                <span class="checkmark">✓</span>
                Instant triage across 8+ platforms
            </div>
            <div class="proof-point">
                <span class="checkmark">✓</span>
                Rule-based + LLM hybrid intelligence
            </div>
            <div class="proof-point">
                <span class="checkmark">✓</span>
                Safe by default (dry-run mode)
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal">
            <div class="terminal-inner">
                <div class="terminal-header">
                    <div class="terminal-title">
                        <span>⌘</span>
                        warp terminal
                    </div>
                    <div class="live-badge">live signals</div>
                </div>
                <div class="command-grid">
                    <div class="command-card">
                        <code class="command">$ make triage T="production outage"</code>
                        <p class="command-output">Classification: bug / critical / negative</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="command-card">
                        <code class="command">$ make query Q="refund policy"</code>
                        <p class="command-output">Searching knowledge base...</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="command-card">
                        <code class="command">$ warp search zendesk urgent</code>
                        <p class="command-output">Found 12 urgent tickets needing attention</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="command-card">
                        <code class="command">$ make status</code>
                        <p class="command-output">8 integrations configured and ready</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-label">Supported Platforms</p>
        </div>
        <div class="integrations">
            <span class="integration-badge">Zendesk</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Intercom</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Freshdesk</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Salesforce Service Cloud</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">HubSpot Service Hub</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Jira Service Management</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Front</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Help Scout</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Slack</span>
            <span class="integration-badge">Notion</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="capabilities" class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-label">Capabilities</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">Built for the work that keeps support teams moving.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Smart Triage</h3>
                <p class="card-body">Automatically classify tickets by category (billing, bug, access, how-to), severity (critical, high, medium, low), sentiment, and language.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🔀</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Intelligent Routing</h3>
                <p class="card-body">Route to L1, L2 technical, billing, privacy/legal, integrations, or product feedback queues based on classification and rules.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">✍️</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Reply Drafting</h3>
                <p class="card-body">Generate customer-facing replies and internal notes with proper tone, multilingual support (EN/PT), and next-step recommendations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">📚</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Knowledge Search</h3>
                <p class="card-body">Search local markdown knowledge base for macros, policies, troubleshooting guides, and best practices to inform responses.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">⏱️</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">SLA Management</h3>
                <p class="card-body">Calculate and track SLAs automatically (1h critical, 4h high, 24h medium, 72h low) with human escalation flags.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🔒</div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Safe Execution</h3>
                <p class="card-body">All mutations default to dry-run mode. Explicit --execute flag required for external system changes. Self-hosted and private.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-label">Quick Start</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">Install and run in minutes.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Via Homebrew (coming soon)</h3>
                <div class="command-card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <code class="command">$ brew tap maio-labs/tap<br>$ brew install warp</code>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Manual Install</h3>
                <div class="command-card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <code class="command">$ git clone https://github.com/ruimachado-orbit/warp<br>$ cd warp<br>$ make setup<br>$ make dev</code>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-label">Results</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-4">
            <div class="card">
                <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">15/15</div>
                <p class="card-body">tests passing with 100% classification accuracy</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">&lt; 500ms</div>
                <p class="card-body">end-to-end orchestration without LLM</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">8+</div>
                <p class="card-body">major helpdesk platforms supported</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">MIT</div>
                <p class="card-body">open source, auditable, self-hosted</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p class="footer-text">
                Built with ❤️ using <a href="https://github.com/anthropics/agent-factory" class="footer-link">Agent Factory</a>
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text">
                © 2026 Maio Labs. MIT License.
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
